.el .ds Aq '
.TH DELPHI-WATERMARK 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
watermark \- Composite a watermark onto an image
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBwatermark\fR <\fB\-\-mark\fR> [\fB\-\-position\fR] [\fB\-\-opacity\fR] [\fB\-\-scale\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIIMAGES\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Composite a watermark onto an image
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-mark\fR \fI<MARK>\fR
Watermark image
.TP
\fB\-\-position\fR \fI<POSITION>\fR [default: bottom\-right]
Position: top\-left, top, top\-right, left, center, right, bottom\-left, bottom, bottom\-right
.TP
\fB\-\-opacity\fR \fI<OPACITY>\fR [default: 0.3]
Opacity 0.0 – 1.0
.TP
\fB\-\-scale\fR \fI<SCALE>\fR [default: 0.2]
Watermark scale relative to the longest edge of the input image
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIIMAGES\fR]

